{
  "texts": [
    "Concretely, we also propose to adapt in our approach integer-based, search space discretization, least-to-most prompting [47] and decision transformer-style [4] fitness improvement queries.",
    "Our experiments demonstrate that our proposed prompting strategy is sufficient to induce the LLM to conduct a recombination operation.",
    "The resulting EvoLLM successfully performs black-box optimization (BBO) on both synthetic BBOB [12] test functions and small neuroevolution tasks [1,19] with various search space dimensions and evaluation budgets (see Figure 1, right).",
    "Furthermore, we provide rigorous ablation to the prompt design and provide general construction recommendations promoting better optimization behavior.",
    "Interestingly, we observe that among our selection of LLMs, there is a general trend indicating that smaller LLM models tend to outperform larger ones."
  ]
}